ZH: 你到底要买什么？一体是怎么回事？
EN: What exactly do you want to buy? What on earth is going on?

ZH: 这个问题一体该怎么解决？
EN: How on earth should this problem be resolved?

ZH: 他一体为什么要辞职？
EN: Why on earth did he resign?

ZH: 我一体忘了把钥匙带在身上。
EN: I forgot to bring the key with me. How could I be so absent-minded?

ZH: 这个任务一体需要多长时间才能完成？
EN: How long on earth does it take to complete this task?

ZH: 你一体为什么要挨饿？
EN: Why on earth did you go hungry?

ZH: 他一体为什么会迟到？
EN: How on earth did he end up being late?

ZH: 这个房间一体是谁设计的？
EN: Who on earth designed this room?

ZH: 我一体从哪里找到这本书？
EN: Where on earth did I find this book?

ZH: 你一体打算怎样解决这个问题？
EN: How on earth do you plan to solve this problem?

ZH: 他一体哪里去了？好像消失无踪。
EN: Where on earth did he go? He seems to have disappeared without a trace.

ZH: 这些动物一体是如何适应严寒的气候的？
EN: How on earth do these animals adapt to the harsh climate?

ZH: 这个试验一体怎么操作？
EN: How on earth do we operate this experiment?

ZH: 他一体做了什么，让你这么生气？
EN: What on earth did he do to make you so angry?

ZH: 这个电子设备一体是如何工作的？
EN: How on earth does this electronic device work?

ZH: 他一体哪里去了？找遍全城都找不到。
EN: Where on earth did he go? We've searched the whole city and can't find him.

ZH: 这个电影一体是谁拍摄的？
EN: Who on earth directed this film?

ZH: 这个地方一体到底是有什么特别之处？
EN: What on earth is so special about this place?

ZH: 你一体以为你是谁？凭什么对我这样说话？
EN: Who on earth do you think you are? How dare you speak to me like this?

ZH: 这个护肤产品一体能不能解决我的皮肤问题？
EN: Can this skincare product actually solve my skin problems?
